{"tid":1555241,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【反送中版】琴日Ruby鬧得我好岩","createTime":"2019-09-09T09:42:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-09T10:34:26.000Z","uid":92277,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"0461a9495f2c8538c2b97551c86bdd8dd3f3c8cc","tid":1555241,"uid":92277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T09:42:09.000Z","msg":"係，我係一個唔值得原諒既仆街！我以為反送中除左遊行就乜都唔洗做，原來仲有好多野可以做！<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">失敗唔係無人撐，係因為無人知</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n希望每人每日做多少少，200萬人每人再搵1個friend已經有半個香港！<br />\n<br />\n文宣我認為係難道最低而又可以幫到成個運動既一件事。<span style=\"color: gold;\">其實整圖既巴打唔介意人地偷圖，只會怪人睇完唔forward! </span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">唔識整圖既大家，我有三樣野希望大家幫幫手</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">1.分享去 Facebook IG Whatsapp Gp </span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n連登接觸面唔夠廣，而且留得係到既已經係跟得好貼既人。希望大家見到靚既文宣，由其<span style=\"color: red;\">行動post</span>，幫一幫手做多步，repost 埋上ig, facebook, WhatsApp 之類既社交評台。一人拉多一個人去遊行就已經多好多。<br />\n<br />\n原文：<br />\n<br />\n200萬人有幾多個真係睇連登<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1542401\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1542401</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">2. 貼連儂牆</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n雖然依家科技發達，但仲有好多人無辦法係果到收到信息。平時我等車都會望到好多叔叔望下牆。其實佢真係好吸睛，都係直接文宣既好地方!<br />\n<br />\n**建議組隊進行，放工放學咪貼兩張。<br />\n**如要去廠印刷，落單要開新Account <br />\n<br />\n原post:<br />\n老母一句屌醒左我，駁唔到。。<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1546699\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1546699</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n文宣組入！印刷都會出事！<br />\n<a href=\"http://lih.kg/dPQbDT\" target=\"_blank\">http://lih.kg/dPQbDT</a><br />\n#1 回覆 - 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">3. Airdrop 比全世界</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n0成本，直接塞信息比人，<span style=\"color: red;\">行動post 優先</span>。平時搭車，行街得閒無野做咪用下！<br />\n<br />\n原post: <br />\n<br />\nIPhone有個咁好用既功能點解要浪費<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1551471\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1551471</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Ld9NuBN.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLd9NuBN.jpg&h=2115e932&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WzQQsos.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWzQQsos.jpg&h=35463d3d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bUOniu8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbUOniu8.jpg&h=ad130f69&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">光復香港，時代革命！光復之日，煲底相聚💛</span>"},{"pid":"6c74acc16adf02446525fe0962174cd386883cc4","tid":1555241,"uid":92277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T09:42:34.000Z","msg":"好啦 見你知錯 原諒你啦😘"},{"pid":"405de420ce1599702f2ea68251ef2e1933f9acdf","tid":1555241,"uid":92277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T09:42:53.000Z","msg":"我會改嫁啦<br />\n日行一善 每日任務"},{"pid":"9de6466ebb03b136f1c4a0eb3ab659cc665076e4","tid":1555241,"uid":92277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T09:43:29.000Z","msg":"屌，打完都打冷震 <br />\n我做咁柒都係想大家幫手炸<br />\n<br />\n求大家每人做多少少呀"},{"pid":"92e0cf1a9597fad9cc3c5a2a19b4481f723a73f8","tid":1555241,"uid":92277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T09:44:32.000Z","msg":"唉又自推10000次<br />\n信唔信我叫奸奸黎陪我推"},{"pid":"8b575d25c3841d0baaa01b861ac6fd87fee1d372","tid":1555241,"uid":92277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T09:44:43.000Z","msg":"9999"},{"pid":"578d8f341823964dd728559ac2de4c1d0f7aa9ed","tid":1555241,"uid":92277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T09:44:54.000Z","msg":"9998"},{"pid":"29f6172a69ae142cf852f08d77143297843984d8","tid":1555241,"uid":92277,